  <brief_title>Comparison of Neuro-navigational Systems for Resection-Control of Brain Tumors</brief_title>
  <official_title>Comparison of Two Neuro-navigational Systems for Resection-control of Intra-axial Brain Tumors. The PoleStarN-20 Intra-operative Magnet Resonance Imager and the Mison SonoWand Intra-operative Ultrasound System</official_title>
